Class QTreeNode

java.lang.Object
  |

        |
        +--com.esri.mo2.data.qb.QTreeNode
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cloneable, MutableTreeNode, Serializable, TreeNode
public class QTreeNode
extends DefaultMutableTreeNode

This class adds two methods to get/set the nodeType for parsing the query tokens. If we want to stream down the class, we can only re-implemnet the MutableTreeNode interface.

See Also:
QueryBuilder, QSyntaxException, Serialized Form
